{
  "stem": "27767.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took us to the ghetto in Baia-Mare, which was the bigger ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was near the-- there was a big factory there, chemical factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the ghetto was right near that chemical factory, on a big piece of land there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, there were some camp-- some barracks there already, but open barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we tried to make some camps there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were there about-- in there, we had-- they were going out all kind of rumors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they spread the rumors, actually, the Hungarian authorities, the German and Hungarian authorities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They spread rumors there that we are going to be taken to mainland Hungary, to the main part of Hungary, to some labor camps until the war is over, and all kinds of rumors like that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I find out later, some families-- a few families in Baia-Mare, they poisoned themselves before they took the them into the ghetto, I think three or four families.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So probably, they were-- maybe they knew something already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know them personally actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto we were-- in the ghetto, we had-- we had an open barrack there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the bunk bed or something there, or on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother and father, and the two sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother, no, because he was in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yeah, we did some-- some work there, with the roads, or with the camp doing something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And tied to-- we got some potatoes there, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how-- what-- we cooked some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we try-- made some fire there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think we were there only about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, all the children were there in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there were no activities.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
